* Stack the observations =======================================================
 
// 'genstacks' is the 'StackMe' function for stacking the data frame obs.
* help genstacks

genstacks q10_ Q7_ q13_ q24_ Q25_ /// 
age_yhat_dich_ age_yhat_cont_ ///
socdem_yhat_dich_ socdem_yhat_cont_, rep


